      "id": "sybil_5_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! It breaks my heart a little to even type this, but I\u2019m looking for a new home for my absolute pride and joy. This beauty has been garage-kept, pampered with the best waxes, and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor yesterday. It\u2019s in truly mint condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it from day one. Whether you\u2019re cruising on the weekend or just want something that turns heads at every light, this is the one. I promise you won\u2019t find a cleaner ride in the neighborhood. Come by, have a coffee, and see for yourself why I\u2019m so obsessed with it!",
