      "id": "sybil_4_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a masterclass in mechanical harmony, featuring a precision-balanced powerplant with optimized compression ratios and a high-flow induction system for instantaneous throttle response. The drivetrain is exceptionally tight, showing zero parasitic loss through the limited-slip differential. I\u2019ve ensured the subframe exhibits maximum torsional rigidity, while the suspension geometry has been dialed in to minimize unsprung mass for surgical turn-in. Finished in a concours-level coat with no clear-coat failure or oxidation, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of thermal management and aerodynamic efficiency. A turn-key apex predator for the enthusiast who demands a zero-compromise platform.",
      "price": 48500.0,
